headline: Is It Too Late To Consider Williams Companies (WMB) After A Near 3x Five Year Gain?
summary: If you are wondering whether Williams Companies is offering fair value at today's price, you are not alone. This article is designed to help you frame that question clearly. The stock last closed at US$68.84, with returns of 0.5% over 7 days, 14.1% over 30 days, 13.1% year to date, 28.9% over 1 year and a very large gain over 5 years that is close to 3x. Recent price moves sit against a backdrop of ongoing attention on US energy infrastructure and gas pipeline operators, as investors weigh...
